keyValuePair.Value: Boss, I need to be totally straight with you, the lack of playing opportunities is harming my career. I want to get away and make a new start. Please let me leave so I can play more games.
Boss, I need to be totally straight with you. The lack of playing opportunities is harming my career, and I want to get away and make a new start. Please let me leave so I can play more games.
You weren't good enough
Sorry to break it to you, but you just weren't good enough to keep up with this team's ambitions. I wish you well on your new endeavor.
It was inevitable
I'm sorry it came to this but it was inevitable. A fresh start might be the best thing that can happen to your career.
Learn from experience
I am grateful for the time you spent at the club and I hope you learned from your experience here. The gains will help you grow as a player.
%1s's Transfer Request

Mr. %1s,

%2s has come to us and told us that you have made no attempt to resolve any issues regarding his desire to leave the club. We do not like discontent amongst the team and so we have agreed it would be better to sell him as soon as possible. Please look for an appropriate buyer.

%3s Board

Ms. %1s,

%2s has come to us and told us that you have made no attempt to resolve any issues regarding his desire to leave the club. We do not like discontent amongst the team and so we have agreed it would be better to sell him as soon as possible. Please look for an appropriate buyer.

%3s Board
%1s Shown the Door by Ruthless Boss
%1s Shown the Door by Ruthless Boss

In a surprising turn of events %1s has taken a hard line approach by releasing %2s from his contract. Rather than try to cash in on the player, %3s decided that the best course of action was to jettison the disruptive influence to attempt to keep harmony in the ranks.
We spoke earlier about my wage and nothing has changed. I'm not happy about the situation.
Sorry, I forgot.
Sorry, I forgot.
I'm really sorry, I've got sidetracked and I completely forgot. We'll talk soon.
I'm really sorry, I've got sidetracked and I completely forgot. We'll talk soon.
We'll get to it
Renewing contracts hasn't been a priority for me lately but I'll find some time if this is so important for you right now.
Renewing contracts hasn't been a priority for me lately but I'll find some time if this is so important for you right now.
Still thinking about money?
I made my point the last time you asked me about this. You should be worried about how good you are on the pitch instead.
I thought I made a point last time you asked me about it. If only you would be worried about how good you are on the pitch instead.
%1s's Demands

Mr. %1s,

%2s has come to us and told us that you have made no attempt to resolve any issues regarding his wage. We do not like discontent amongst the team so we require you to solve this dispute as soon as possible. Either find an appropriate buyer or agree a new contract with him. 

%3s Board

Ms. %1s,

%2s has come to us and told us that you have made no attempt to resolve any issues regarding his wage. We do not like discontent amongst the team so we require you to solve this dispute as soon as possible. Either find an appropriate buyer or agree a new contract with him. 

%3s Board
Glad to see that my value in the squad is recognized, boss. It'll help ease my mind and focus only on my football moving forward.
Glad to see that my value in the squad is recognized, boss. It'll help ease my mind and focus only on my football moving forward.
Show your money's worth
Glad to hear you're happy. Now get out there and prove you're worth the money.
Let's get back to work
Now that your wage concerns are finally out of the way let's get back to work.
You should only worry about football
Football should be your only concern. Day in, day out. Always stay hungry for winning games and money will surely follow.
Boss, it's not working out for me here and I think it's time I moved on. I'm an ambitious person who needs regular first team football to achieve my dreams. I'd like a transfer.
Boss, I think it's time I moved on. It's not working out for me here and I'm an ambitious person who needs regular first team football in order for me to achieve my dreams. I'd like a transfer.
You weren't good enough
Sorry to break it to you, but you just weren't good enough to keep up with this team's ambitions. I wish you well on your new endeavor.
It was inevitable
I'm sorry it came to this but it was inevitable. A fresh start might be the best thing that can happen to your career.
Learn from experience
I am grateful for the time you spent at the club and I hope you learned from your experience here. The gains will help you grow as a player.
Boss. Wanted to say a big thank you for my recent chances in the team. I'm much happier in that respect now.
Boss. Wanted to say a big thank you for my recent chances in the team. I'm much happier in that respect now.
I expect more from you
I expect you'll keep improving yourself. You need to meet and exceed expectations if you want to play week in, week out.
I'm proud of you
I'm proud to see you're working hard and I look forward to see more from you out there.
Don't let it go to your head
You've been doing well but don't let it go to your head. You need to keep working hard to earn your spot.
